Video Script for Census Income Prediction Project
Introduction (0:00 - 0:30)
[Opening Scene: Presenter in front of a computer with the dataset on the screen]
Hello everyone! Welcome to my presentation on the Census Income Prediction project. In this project, we aim to predict whether an individual's income exceeds $50,000 per year based on various demographic factors. This is a fascinating application of machine learning that can provide insights into income distribution and help identify trends in socioeconomic status.
